 />"},{"pid":"129798524ca2b9d9b8d699711895423d073face6","tid":2469432,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T19:59:44.000Z","msg":"車 洗撚咩<br />\n番左香港既唔認罪咪又係上面果兩個受"},{"pid":"a88725a0e2270766b5799a7423b5a9bc5fa1c9ba","tid":2469432,"uid":76728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"804ee6ff92738e2b5da2b9a5435648f8b6b4119f","tid":2469432,"uid":271434,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T13:21:45.000Z","msg":"港共如果話李宇軒轉做污點證人而又唔俾人探訪佢嘅話，大家可以相信呢個一定係假嘅李宇軒，真&middot;李宇軒已經俾中共或者港共殺咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T23:12:02.000Z","msg":"好多原因唔俾見嘅，唔一定係死咗。<br />\n<br />\n共產黨係分化嘅專家，安穩在家嘅你我都可以被分化，更何況係面對緊囚徒困境嘅12人。當初要坐舢舨出逃就係缺乏安全感，而家直情俾兩地公安攞鎗指住然後囚禁咗幾個月，果種恐懼同折磨你哋真係體會到？<br />\n<br />\n咁嘅情況下屈服其實唔出奇，要記住李宇軒只係一個普通嘅香港人，佢唔係007；要記住極權最擅長屈打成招。<br />\n<br />\n而無論佢有無被屈打成招，囚徒困境嘅核心就係訊息被隔絕，只要新聞報咗李宇軒嘅事，其他人就會開始猜疑，最後佢本人亦可能會動搖。<br />\n<br />\n而為咗隔絕訊息，12人都唔會收到港共以外發佈嘅訊息，唔好話見家人，信都未必收到。"},{"pid":"23e70092b63a7ca29656e6a7ceec1ebee25d2ed8","tid":2469432,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T10:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e66452658b33dc224ddc779391b141cd9e94de","tid":2469432,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T07:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e84d6240b8adee92a90897e6533687e3b79a258","tid":2469432,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T07:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse